{"title":"关于Java中length、length()、size()的区别","date":"2018-10-10T03:57:47.000Z","link":"post/268","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:43:01.822Z","content":"<h3 id=\"length不是方法，是属性，数组的属性；\">length不是方法，是属性，数组的属性；<a href=\"post/268#length不是方法，是属性，数组的属性；\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span>[] intArray = &#123;<span class=\"number\">1</span>,<span class=\"number\">2</span>,<span class=\"number\">3</span>&#125;;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"这个数组的长度为：\"</span> + intArray.length);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"length-是字符串String的一个方法；\">length()是字符串String的一个方法；<a href=\"post/268#length-是字符串String的一个方法；\"></a></h3><figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tString str = <span class=\"string\">\"HelloWorld\"</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">\tSystem.out.println(<span class=\"string\">\"这个字符串的长度为：\"</span> + str.length());</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n<h3 id=\"size-方法，是List集合的一个方法；\">size()方法，是List集合的一个方法；<a href=\"post/268#size-方法，是List集合的一个方法；\"></a></h3><p><code>`</code>java<br>public static void main(String[] args) {</p>\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; list = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\n\nlist.add(&quot;a&quot;);\n\nlist.add(&quot;b&quot;);\n\nlist.add(&quot;c&quot;);\n\nSystem.out.println(&quot;这个list的长度为：&quot; + list.size());\n</code></pre>","prev":{"title":"Java数据类型中String、Integer、int相互间的转换","link":"post/269"},"next":{"title":"Oracle中date错误，ORA-01830: date format picture ends before converting entire input string","link":"post/266"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/268/"}